sudo pacman -S gparted lxappearance terminology guake playerctl pacman-contrib ranger arandr dialog numlockx mtools dosfstools network-manager-applet wpa_supplicant bluez bluez-utils cups gvfs arc-gtk-theme papirus-icon-theme ttf-font-awesome galculator qt5ct ttf-jetbrains-mono nitrogen os-prober wqy-zenhei cmatrix cowsay lolcat doge figlet asciiquarium rofi-emoji spotifyd stack ttf-liberation reflector bash-completion unzip gimp libreoffice btop

